ull,"type":null,"assignees":[],"labels":[]},{"id":"26898a3e-9df1-4b85-8c16-00c37921794e","type_id":null,"created_at":"2026-04-29T22:57:15.550582+02:00","updated_at":"2026-04-29T22:57:15.779023+02:00","deleted_at":null,"point":null,"name":"Quick actions pro zakázky","description_html":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph-block\" data-id=\"22f58bfc-6ab3-4d36-949e-95eca7c5b2b4\">V seznamu zakázek přidat ke každé zakázce i archivované na konec řádku ikonu tří teček, ve které by byli quick actions pro zakázky, takže rychlý proklik do editace nebo smazání, archivace, dearchivace, rychlé nahrání souboru, něco takového, pokud tě ještě něco napadne, tak se zeptej a nějak to vymslíme</p>","description_binary":null,"priority":"low","start_date":null,"target_date":null,"sequence_id":30,"sort_order":345535.0,"completed_at":null,"archived_at":null,"is_draft":false,"external_source":null,"external_id":null,"created_by":"6d2ea97e-abcf-423e-8d71-e64127c7d53c","updated_by":null,"project":"7f795ffa-ac93-4f40-87b2-7cb96f4bbb39","workspace":"0e52b124-6c65-47d3-a9fd-409bb2ae0236","parent":"ce0c0028-685f-4d1b-89d3-fc10e37b632f","state":"1a6358ee-15a9-44bb-b7c8-5a604b794aeb","estimate_point":null,"type":null,"assignees":[],"labels":[]},{"id":"8a1f7abd-934e-4db0-ad95-36ce73c9c248","type_id":null,"created_at":"2026-04-29T22:49:12.840404+02:00","updated_at":"2026-04-29T22:55:07.806133+02:00","deleted_at":null,"point":null,"name":"Edit zakázky","description_html":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph-block\" data-id=\"7a96085e-dc8b-4528-ac53-0a6868b1a11d\">V editaci zakázky máme více tlačítek na krok zpět na detail zakázky, udělej jen jedno a dej ho do leva nahoru před název zakázky</p><p class=\"editor-paragraph-block\" data-id=\"418cd9ef-db26-4871-8db5-f8a33e3cb911\"></p><p class=\"editor-paragraph-block\" data-id=\"da3b8ba8-5e99-495a-bfe5-d32f877aab77\">Všeobecně tam je moc tlačítek, mají různé barvy, nějak to chce sjednotit</p><p class=\"editor-paragraph-block\" data-id=\"56bc137b-f2fa-40dc-857c-f0b6d67efa06\">Udělat širší pole na název projetku</p><p class=\"editor-paragraph-block\" data-id=\"140373eb-a3a5-44ed-9f39-41a8b03b57b9\"></p><p class=\"editor-paragraph-block\" data-id=\"f98c8d23-869a-4370-9cfb-3071dd2c240f\">Možná dát pryč ten hint s smazáním a archivací, je to takový zbytečný, a zobrazit tlačítko na smazání až po archivaci.</p>","description_binary":null,"priority":"none","start_date":null,"target_date":null,"sequence_id":29,"sort_order":335535.0,"completed_at":null,"archived_at":null,"is_draft":false,"external_source":null,"external_id":null,"created_by":"6d2ea97e-abcf-423e-8d71-e64127c7d53c","updated_by":"6d2ea97e-abcf-423e-8d71-e64127c7d53c","project":"7f795ffa-ac93-4f40-87b2-7cb96f4bbb39","workspace":"0e52b124-6c65-47d3-a9fd-409bb2ae0236","parent":"ce0c0028-685f-4d1b-89d3-fc10e37b632f","state":"1a6358ee-15a9-44bb-b7c8-5a604b794aeb","estimate_point":null,"type":null,"assignees":[],"labels":[]},{"id":"48d8b153-8dc6-4ed3-b6ad-71ed4f43889f","type_id":null,"created_at":"2026-04-29T22:47:20.315036+02:00","updated_at":"2026-04-29T22:47:20.561768+02:00","deleted_at":null,"point":null,"name":"Zadavatel","description_html":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph-block\" data-id=\"142026f7-527c-4d7f-b6e6-dd40389e910a\">Přidat možnost zde mít telefonní číslo (bude hezky naformátované jako v detailu zaměstnance) a email. Oboje se bude vkládat v editaci zakázky nebo přímo při vytváření zakázky. Pole pro telefonní číslo si vem z detailu zaměstnance.</p>","description_binary":null,"priority":"medium","start_date":null,"target_date":null,"sequence_id":28,"sort_order":325535.0,"completed_at":null,"archived_at":null,"is_draft":false,"external_source":null,"external_id":null,"created_by":"6d2ea97e-abcf-423e-8d71-e64127c7d53c","updated_by":null,"project":"7f795ffa-ac93-4f40-87b2-7cb96f4bbb39","workspace":"0e52b124-6c65-47d3-a9fd-409bb2ae0236","parent":"ce0c0028-685f-4d1b-89d3-fc10e37b632f","state":"1a6358ee-15a9-44bb-b7c8-5a604b794aeb","estimate_point":null,"type":null,"assignees":[],"labels":[]},{"id":"61e859f5-6cd1-4b25-94b6-482461dcc148","type_id":null,"created_at":"2026-04-29T22:45:30.920854+02:00","updated_at":"2026-04-29T22:45:31.149969+02:00","deleted_at":null,"point":null,"name":"Shortcut do mapy","description_html":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph-block\" data-id=\"8a1ffe95-67b4-4cd4-9573-82e300e2e57a\">Když kliknu v detailu zakázky na tag adresy, tak bych chtěl, aby se mi v nové záložce otevřeli google mapy s adresou, na kterou jsem klik</p>","description_binary":null,"priority":"low","start_date":null,"target_date":null,"sequence_id":27,"sort_order":315535.0,"completed_at":null,"archived_at":null,"is_draft":false,"external_source":null,"external_id":null,"created_by":"6d2ea97e-abcf-423e-8d71-e64127c7d53c","updated_by":null,"project":"7f795ffa-ac93-4f40-87b2-7cb96f4bbb39","workspace":"0e52b124-6c65-47d3-a9fd-409bb2ae0236","parent":"ce0c0028-685f-4d1b-89d3-fc10e37b632f","state":"1a6358ee-15a9-44bb-b7c8-5a604b794aeb","estimate_point":null,"type":null,"assignees":[],"labels":[]},{"id":"af9d2bc9-9cb2-4e1e-b288-f851d3384768","type_id":null,"created_at":"2026-04-29T22:43:08.261426+02:00","updated_at":"2026-04-29T22:43:08.488236+02:00","deleted_at":null,"point":null,"name":"Rozpočet zakázky","description_html":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph-block\" data-id=\"e0ed16b6-3ecc-4ebc-b5d6-1ef8a35113ef\">Zde bych defaultně schoval tlačítka a input na změnu budgetu, pomocí nového tlačítka se input a stará tlačika zobrazí / schovají</p>","description_binary":null,"priority":"medium","start_date":null,"target_date":null,"sequence_id":26,"sort_order":305535.0,"completed_at":null,"archived_at":null,"is_draft":false,"external_source":null,"external_id":null,"created_by":"6d2ea97e-abcf-423e-8d71-e64127c7d53c","updated_by":null,"project":"7f795ffa-ac93-4f40-87b2-7cb96f4bbb39","workspace":"0e52b124-6c65-47d3-a9fd-409bb2ae0236","parent":"ce0c0028-685f-4d1b-89d3-fc10e37b632f","state":"1a6358ee-15a9-44bb-b7c8-5a604b794aeb","estimate_point":null,"type":null,"assignee